      <title>希腊将派遣护卫舰前往红海保护航运</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/greece-send-frigate-red-sea-protect-shipping-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊周四表示，在也门伊朗支持的胡塞武装发动袭击后，将派遣一艘海军护卫舰前往红海保护航运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/greece-send-frigate-red-sea-protect-shipping-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:59:16 GMT</pubDate>
