      <title>驱逐俄罗斯军队一年后，乌克兰小镇面临严冬</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukrainian-town-faces-tough-winter-year-after-driving-out-russian-forces-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰东部小镇莱曼遭受重创，仅存的少数居民正在为降雪和气温下降的艰难冬季做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukrainian-town-faces-tough-winter-year-after-driving-out-russian-forces-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 07:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
